  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to btrfs-progs</title>

    <para>The <application>btrfs-progs</application> package contains administration
    and debugging tools for the B-tree file system (btrfs).</para>

    &lfs79_checked;
    &gcc6_checked;

